P’kk is a lesser deity of the Neogi Pantheon. It&nbsp;is the favorite deity of
captains and neogi in positions of power who enjoy bullying and
manipulating their lessers. P’kk is seen as an umber hulk with the head
of a neogi.
P'kk is lawful evil. It dwells in Baator, which the neogi call Ki'pik.
Source: Jon Winter, "The Ecology of the Neogi," in Dragon Magazine #214&nbsp;</span> </p>